293
00:25:58,166 --> 00:26:00,125
[pattering of heavy rain]

294
00:26:02,166 --> 00:26:04,166
[ominous music plays]

295
00:26:26,041 --> 00:26:27,375
You traveled with that?

296
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,625
[mechanism whirs]

297
00:26:39,416 --> 00:26:41,208
It's the last one I have.

298
00:26:43,208 --> 00:26:45,916
It's the only way I can go back again.

299
00:27:05,208 --> 00:27:06,666
[buzz, thud]

300
00:27:09,083 --> 00:27:10,083
[door opens]

301
00:27:12,291 --> 00:27:13,958
[door squeaks and closes]

302
00:27:14,708 --> 00:27:17,125
[two dramatic metallic beats sound]

303
00:27:21,708 --> 00:27:23,416
[heartbeat like thud]

304
00:27:25,166 --> 00:27:26,916
[quiet ticking]

305
00:27:33,958 --> 00:27:36,875
You could have told him
which path you would send him down.

306
00:27:39,708 --> 00:27:40,958
How it'll end.

307
00:27:43,125 --> 00:27:46,875
Even if he knows, he will never stop
trying to break the cycle.

308
00:27:49,083 --> 00:27:50,208
He won't understand...

309
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:54,166
that we must preserve the knot.

310
00:27:57,375 --> 00:27:58,791
That his Martha must perish.

311
00:28:01,208 --> 00:28:03,416
So that all others can live.

312
00:28:04,708 --> 00:28:06,625
[mysterious, unsettling music plays]

313
00:28:25,500 --> 00:28:26,666
The beginning...

314
00:28:28,458 --> 00:28:29,541
and the end.

315
00:28:29,625 --> 00:28:31,791
WINDEN NUCLEAR POWER PLANT
VOLUME CONTROL SYSTEM

316
00:28:31,875 --> 00:28:34,875
[metallic beats resume]

317
00:28:38,208 --> 00:28:40,625
[unsettling music
