321
00:29:34,958 --> 00:29:36,583
Ulrich, it's me, Charlotte. I...

322
00:29:38,291 --> 00:29:40,166
I just wanted to know you're all right.

323
00:29:41,458 --> 00:29:42,708
Call me here, okay?

324
00:29:48,791 --> 00:29:49,666
[sighs]

325
00:29:54,708 --> 00:29:56,750
]bolts clatter]

326
00:29:56,833 --> 00:29:57,916
[hatch creaks]

327
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,041
[hatch clatters]

328
00:30:00,125 --> 00:30:02,125
