00:31:44,208 --> 00:31:47,333
[ominous music intensifies]

339
00:31:56,791 --> 00:32:00,083
[ominous music intensifies]

340
00:32:03,166 --> 00:32:05,166
[wind whistling]

341
00:32:33,166 --> 00:32:34,166
Can I see Kilian?

342
00:32:37,375 --> 00:32:38,208
Kilian.

343
00:32:50,083 --> 00:32:50,916
Hey.

344
00:32:53,125 --> 00:32:53,958
Hey.

345
00:32:56,125 --> 00:32:57,041
