About Regina...

365
00:34:42,291 --> 00:34:43,291
I'm sorry.

366
00:34:46,125 --> 00:34:47,625
It must be difficult for you.

367
00:34:50,875 --> 00:34:51,958
How are you?

368
00:34:54,625 --> 00:34:55,833
Bartosz?

369
00:34:56,791 --> 00:34:58,125
